{"tid":1530313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幾時大家一齊去幫趁黨鐵商場？","createTime":"2019-09-02T02:26:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T04:02:16.000Z","uid":132999,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"971c7375e09a422eecabeecb8cfbd4079fca61d2","tid":1530313,"uid":132999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T02:26:58.000Z","msg":"呢個 weekend 行山行到好攰<br />\n不如下個星期一齊行下街輕鬆下？<br />\n<br />\n名單如下（歡迎自行更新）<br />\n-沙田連城廣場Citylink<br />\n-火炭駿景廣場<br />\n-屯門恆福商場<br />\n-屯門海趣坊<br />\n-屯門新屯門商場<br />\n-將軍澳PopCorn 1<br />\n-將軍澳PopCorn 2<br />\n-坑口連理街<br />\n-荃灣綠楊坊<br />\n-九龍圓方<br />\n-奧運奧海城一、二期<br />\n-九龍灣德福廣場<br />\n-青衣青衣城<br />\n-杏花邨杏花新城<br />\n-柴灣新翠商場<br />\n不要睇小個人力量，團結必然事成！<br />\n香港人已經失去太多，再不能失去更多！"},{"pid":"fec8baa300342ac0f2b296daaa9c2291da65264f","tid":1530313,"uid":132999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T02:27:13.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"cf6f3124d414c2eeb88c692bb09aac9ffea2cd7c","tid":1530313,"uid":132999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T02:27:24.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"2f197342cd0489d90bb114ea67ec0f7dd12f41f6","tid":1530313,"uid":132999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T02:27:34.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"cac340d046d5591ee7c3b86b4eb897e340930899","tid":1530313,"uid":132999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T02:27:49.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"6e6081a1a3382a217663716005835a1e03f4201f","tid":1530313,"uid":132999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T02:28:00.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"ff5e314d28b0a2872b11d1d8b12253b950b07384","tid":1530313,"uid":132999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T02:28:13.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"ed42f11dd653d44eecb986d18812f6b783b0cb24","tid":1530313,"uid":132999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T02:29:34.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"7a74b6932aef4ed82df885fac97f6cc9dc21bd5e","tid":1530313,"uid":